Only August 27: The Japanese box office hit Detective Conan: The Million Dollar Pentagram

In Hakodate, Hokkaido, Kaito Kid´s business card has turned up in an Onoe Group warehouse, causing immediate excitement and concern over his famous thefts. At the same time, a body with a slashed cross on its chest is found in the warehouse district, leading investigators to a notorious arms dealer of Japanese descent and American heritage.

Starting September 12: The long-awaited sequel to Burton’s award-winning Beetlejuice.

Beetlejuice Beetlejuice (OV)

Beetlejuice is back! After an unexpected family tragedy, three generations of the Deetz family return to Winter River. Lydia, still haunted by Beetlejuice, finds her life thrown into disarray when her rebellious teenage daughter Astrid discovers the mysterious model of the town in the attic and the gate to the world of the dead is inadvertently opened. Disaster is brewing both in this world and the next.
